<ul>
    <li><font size="4">Video Databases: What is needed?<br>
        <br>
        There two basic operations for very data management
        system: <br>
        (1) suitable data structuring for its representation and
        organization; <br>
        (2) data indexing and retrieval.<br>
        <br>
        Data Representation<br>
        The spatio-temporal nature of the video data requires
        spacial attention. Video can be represented at multiple
        levels.</font><br>
        </li>
</ul>

<blockquote>
    <table border="4" cellpadding="2">
        <tr>
            <td><p align="center"><font color="#800000">Level</font>
