<ul>
    <li><p align="left"><font size="4">Video Data Indexing:
        content based and similarity based<br>
        Videos --&gt; smaller atomic units.<br>
        Video clips + Label: future search and retrieval<br>
        Video indexing: labeling video clips<br>
        <img src="f55.jpg" hspace="20" vspace="20" width="525"
        height="338"><br>
        Content-based indexing: based on human psychology of
        remembering and recollecting information. e.g., People
        try to recall a person by their description such as tall,
        gray hair, blue eyes, long nose, etc.<br>
        Implementation: Manual, Semiautomatic or fully automatic.<br>
        <br>
        Similarity-based indexing: an natural extensions to the
        image database's similarity retrieval research.
        Feature-based indexing is used in many indexing schemes.<br>
        </font></p>
        <hr>
    </li>
</ul>

